 Pacifica 67, La Quinta 58 -- Jon Surface scored 21 points and Chris Vlasic 
added 14 for host Pacifica (21-1, 12-0). Kevin Doane scored 16 points for La 
Quinta (13-10, 7-5). 
</P>
