scored 16 points for Cerritos Valley Christian (10-11, 7-3). Jeff Jennings 
scored 10 points for Capistrano Valley Christian (3-18, 1-8). 
</P>
<P>
 Ontario Christian 75, Orange Lutheran 73 (OT) -- Kyle Salyer's base-line 
jumper at the buzzer sent the game into overtime and Armen Bagatourian's three 
three-pointers in overtime kept Orange Lutheran within striking distance before 
falling. Bagatourian finished with 17 points, Tom Howard added 15 points, 
