<HEADLINE>
<P>
COLLEGE ROUNDUP; FULLERTON WRESTLERS TOP SAN FRANCISCO STATE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Cal State Fullerton won seven of 10 matches, led by Chris Abrego's pin at 177 
pounds, to defeat San Francisco State, 28-12, Friday in nonconference 
wrestling. 
</P>
