 Grant 76, Sherman Oaks CES 36 -- Ronald (18) and Donald (12) Patterson 
combined for 30 points as four Lancer players reached double figures. Alvin 
Castro scored 17 points and grabbed 10 rebounds for Grant (14-3, 5-0), which 
remained undefeated in Valley Pac-8 play. 
</P>
<P>
