 His guilty plea came Thursday after the prosecutor handling the case, Deputy 
Dist. Atty. Donna K. Gissing, had given her opening remarks and was preparing 
to introduce testimony. 
</P>
<P>
 Edwards' attorney, Deputy Public Defender Stephen P. Lipson, has said his 
client was distraught over the breakup with his longtime girlfriend. 
</P>
