$50,000 of county recreation money for the Boys and Girls Club of Anaheim. 
</P>
<P>
 Mike Sofia, executive director of the Boys and Girls Club, said the money will 
go toward completion of a 5,460-square-foot facility at East Broadway and 
Philadelphia Street. 
</P>
<P>
 "We are very appreciative of Supervisor Steiner's efforts," he said. "This 
will go a long way towards helping us move forward with our new club facility." 
</P>
