<TEXT>
<P>
 Vietnam strategy -- A story in Friday's editions on President Clinton's 
Vietnam strategy incorrectly stated that Sen. John Kerry (D-Mass.) was a 
recipient of the Medal of Honor. Kerry was awarded a Silver Star, a Bronze Star 
and three Purple Hearts during his military service in Vietnam. 
</P>
